<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-10-03T07:00:41-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-10-03T07:00:41-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-03T07:00:41-04:00</updated><title> “WordPress”之争现已升级为诉讼</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;WordPress 徽标的矢量插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/6-kXfzcdEuq0ho1UDDUfOW2wXOw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73628745/STK302_WORDPRESS.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;WP Engine 表示，该诉讼旨在解决“滥用权力、勒索和贪婪”问题。&lt;/em>; |图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;S1LFTo&quot;>;WP Engine 网络托管服务在公开争吵后起诉 WordPress 联合创始人 Matt Mullenweg 和 Automattic 涉嫌诽谤和企图敲诈勒索WordPress 商标和开源项目。在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwpengine.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FComplaint-WP -Engine-v-Automattic-et-al-with-Exhibit.pdf&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F10%2F3%2F24261016%2Fwordpress-wp-engine -lawsuit-automattic-matt-mullenweg&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;周三提起的联邦诉讼&lt;/a>;，WP Engine 指控 Automattic 及其首席执行官 Mullenweg “滥用权力、敲诈勒索和贪婪”，并表示其旨在阻止他们对 WP Engine 和 WordPress 社区造成进一步伤害。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Seu332&quot;>;WP Engine 是 WordPress.com 的主要竞争对手，拥有超过 200,000 个网站使用该服务。 Mullenweg 运营着 Automattic，该公司拥有 WordPress.com，该公司销售开源 WordPress 软件的托管版本 - 就像 WP Engine 一样。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot; >;&lt;aside id=&quot;ad9GRF&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;混乱的 WordPress 戏剧，解释一下 &quot;,&quot; url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24256361/wordpress-wp-engine-drama-explained-matt-mullenweg&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt; /div>; &lt;p id=&quot;Xd2pFh&quot;>;诉讼是在...之后发起的&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/3/24261016/wordpress -wp-engine-lawsuit-automatic-matt-mullenweg&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/3/24261016/wordpress-wp-engine-lawsuit-automattic-matt-mullenweg" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/3/24261016/wordpress-wp-engine-lawsuit-automattic-matt-mullenweg</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-03T03:15:29-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-03T03:15:29-04:00</updated><title>美国银行停电导致客户账户余额被清空</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;钱包的图形照片拼贴。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/9BheYpWLJ1ez7iCIuKghR083Z34=/20x0:2021x1334/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73627482/STK417_MONEY_CVIRGINIA_A.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge； Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;3My7wh&quot;>;首先，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/29/24257477/spotify-outage-down -website-app&quot;>;Spotify&lt;/a>;，然后 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/30/24258362/verizon-mobile-services-down-sos-mode&quot;>;Verizon &lt;/a>;，然后是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/30/24258362/verizon-mobile-services-down-sos-mode&quot;>;PlayStation&lt;/a>;，现在本周显然轮到美国银行发生故障了。周三，一些客户报告访问银行账户时出现问题，余额显示为 0 美元或“----”，而不是应有的内容。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;BMgAVX&quot;>;“今天早些时候，一些移动和在线银​​行客户在访问其账户和余额信息时遇到了问题，”美国银行媒体关系主管 Matt Card 在给 The Verge 的电子邮件中写道&lt;/em>;。 “这些技术问题&lt;strong>;&lt;/strong>;已得到完全解决。对于给您带来的任何不便，我们深表歉意。”&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;TuF9tO&quot;>;在美国东部时间下午 1 点之前，Down detector 上的报告数量激增，帖子遍布 X 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reddit.com/r/ BankOfAmerica/comments/1fuldts/boa_app_and_website_down/&quot;>;Reddit &lt;/a>;来自人们报告说他们的帐户余额没有显示任何内容（有些人提到...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/2024/10/2/24260615/bank-of-america-is-down-outage-account-balance-blank-zero&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/2/24260615/bank-of-america-is-down-outage-account-balance-blank-zero" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/2/24260615/bank-of-america-is-down-outage-account-balance-blank-zero</id><author><name>理查德·劳勒</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-03T03:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-03T03:00:00-04:00</updated><title> Oura Ring 4 具有更纤薄的传感器、更高的精度和更多尺寸</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;桌子上的各种版本的 Oura Ring 4&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/A4ev6G3t2MP5Coy8O1FNnR0s9Zw=/0x0:3840x2560/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn. com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73628574/08_Oura_Ring_4_Product_Imagery.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;戒指有六种颜色。&lt;/em>; |图片：Oura&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;eQszJv&quot;>;Oura 正在对其广受欢迎的智能戒指和应用程序进行重大改造。该公司刚刚发布了售价 349 美元的 Oura Ring 4，它将采用更纤薄的设计、更高的精度和更多尺寸。从今天开始，Oura 应用程序也将进行彻底的重新设计，以更好地组织过去几个月推出的一系列新功能。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;nnbX6q&quot;>;乍一看，Oura Ring 4 并没有“看起来与&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22789248/oura-ring-3-review-sleep-tracker-fitness-tracker&quot;>;Gen 3&lt;/a>;有太大不同。然而，新戒指将完全由钛制成。 （之前的环具有环氧树脂内部。）所有环也将是完全圆形的，例如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/9/28/23377115/oura-horizo​​n-smart- ring-rose-gold-announcement&quot;>;当前 Horizo​​n 型号&lt;/a>;，没有平边。也许最值得注意的是，传感器不再具有突出的圆顶形盖子。相反，它们凹进以获得更平坦、更...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/3/24260260/oura-ring-4-价格规格-智能环-可穿戴&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/3/24260260/oura-ring-4-price-specs-smart-ring-wearable" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/3/24260260/oura-ring-4-price-specs-smart-ring-wearable</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-02T21:28:49-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-02T21:28:49-04:00</updated><title> 500 美元以下可以买到的最好的智能手机</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;来自 Google、Apple 和 Samsung 的手机，背景为彩色插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/t2Mje1exJnZyEZRBhf5hrBEQbvE=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/67732462/226422_K_Radtke_budget_phone_buying_guide.1 3.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;如果您知道如何选择优先事项，现在您就可以花不到 500 美元购买一台出色的设备。&lt;/em>; |图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;你不可能以这个价格拥有一切，但你可以获得一部很棒的智能手机。无论您想要 iPhone、120Hz 屏幕还是防水，您都有选择。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21420196/best-budget-smartphone-便宜&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/21420196/best-budget-smartphone-cheap" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/21420196/best-budget-smartphone-cheap</id><author><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-02T20:23:58-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-02T20:23:58-04:00</updated><title> Ring 刚刚将其针对老客户的警报监控服务价格提高了一倍</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/RhRWmZnyvqu6mgHUOGIpG3TlGME=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73628233 /dseifert_180630_2714_0001.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Dan Seifert / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Zwepm4&quot;>;您是否像我一样购买了&lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/2018/7/3/17530782/ring-alarm-security-system-smart-home-review-price-features&quot;>;适合您家的响铃警报系统&lt;/a>;，因为它提供了最价格实惠的专业 24/7 监控，每月只需 10 美元或每年 100 美元？然后我希望您（像我一样）刚刚收到一封电子邮件，说明您从下次续订时开始将支付两倍的费用。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Uu0P80&quot;>;这是我几个小时前收到的电子邮件的顶部，告诉我从 3 月份开始每月支付 20 美元或每年支付 200 美元，&lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2021/9/28/22692073/ring-alarm-pro-amazon-event-release-date-specs-price-features#:~:text=no%20professional%20monitoring.-,Ring %20Protect%20Pro,-(%2420/mo%20or&quot;>;与亚马逊三年前开始销售的 Ring Protect Pro 计划的价格&lt;/a>;相匹配。我之前使用过 Ring Protect Plus：&lt;/p>; &lt;图class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：Sean Hollister / The Verge&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;价格上涨。&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;div class=&quot;c- float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;YzGP65&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot; Ring 终于在其安全摄像头中添加了 24/7 录制功能&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/2/24259779/ring-24-7-continuous-recording-smart-security -cameras&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;Y23vzu&quot;>;价格上涨总是令人烦恼，但我想，Ring 仍然是一种相对实惠的报警服务。真正令人愤怒的部分：...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/2/24260773/amazon-ring-alarm-price-hike-dark-模式&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/2/24260773/amazon-ring-alarm-price-hike-dark-pattern" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/2/24260773/amazon-ring-alarm-price-hike-dark-pattern</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-02T19:38:17-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-02T19:38:17-04:00</updated><title>这是目前最优惠的 iPad 优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;iPad Pro 放在木桌上。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/SXw6mWFnm2KC-W8TVnliyrauorQ=/0x0:2700x1800/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/66899976/247111_iPad_Pro_2024_AKrales_1080.53 .jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;尽管 Apple 最新的 iPad Pro 才刚刚推出，但它已经以约 100 美元的折扣进行销售。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;BAaqdG&quot;>;虽然最优惠的 iPad 优惠通常会在黑色星期五和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. theverge.com/24255302/amazon-prime-day-deals-tips-news-guide-2024-october&quot;>;亚马逊即将举行 Prime Day 活动